>Bedroom(8)</span></div></button></div><div class="c8yyj-thumbnail"><button class="M11p M11p-mod-no-radius" tabindex="0" aria-label="Other"><img class="ATNn M11p-image" src="/rimg/himg/d5/95/8b/expedia_group-495978-163012275-114893.jpg?width=836&amp;height=607&amp;crop=true" alt="Other Photo"/><div class="M11p-text-container"><span class="M11p-text">Other(6)</span></div></button></div><div class="c8yyj-thumbnail"><button class="M11p M11p-mod-no-radius" tabindex="0" aria-label="Outdoors view"><img class="ATNn M11p-image" src="/rimg/himg/c3/1c/0b/expediav2-495978-99b1ec-382612.jpg?width=836&amp;height=607&amp;crop=true" alt="Outdoors view Photo"/><div class="M11p-text-container"><span class="M11p-text">Outdoors view(4)</span></div></button></div><div class="c8yyj-view-all-photos-button"><button role="button" class="Iqt3 Iqt3-mod-bold Button-No-Standard-Style Iqt3-mod-variant-solid Iqt3-mod-theme-light Iqt3-mod-shape-rounded-small Iqt3-mod-shape-mod-default Iqt3-mod-spacing-default Iqt3-mod-size-default" tabindex="0" aria-disabled="false"><div class="Iqt3-button-container"><div class="Iqt3-button-content">View all photos</div></div><div class="Iqt3-button-focus-outline"></div></button></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div><div role="region" aria-label="Overview" tabindex="-1"><span id="navbar-item-about" class="vlX0-section-scroll-position" style="top:-100px"></span><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><div class="b40a" data-section-name="overview"><div class="b40a-overview b40a-mod-two-column"><div class="b40a-section-headers"><div class="b40a-overview-header"><h2 class="T_-S T_-S-section-header T_-S-mod-overview">Overview</h2></div></div><div class="b40a-overview-sections"><div class="b40a-section-container b40a-overview-container"><div class="b40a-desc-text b40a-mod-contracted"><p>The Alta Hotels The Snowpine Lodge is located on the top of Little Cottonwood Canyon and nestled in the Wasatch Mountains in Alta, Utah. The hotel is only a 30-minute drive from Big Cottonwood Canyon and less than 35 miles from the Salt Lake City International Airport. This hotel was recently renovated in 2017 and offers 78 air-conditioned, non-smoking guestrooms next to Alta Ski Resort.</p>
<p>Lodging options at The Snowpine Lodge range from dorm living to standard rooms, premium rooms, and suites. The hotel has a fitness center and yoga studio with a rowing machine, free weights, stationary bike, treadmills, ellipticals, and a weight machine. There is a heated outdoor pool along with jetted spas, basketball hoops, and a volleyball net for exercise and fun. The hotel also offers outdoor firepits and ski lockers where guests can stow their gear.</p>
<p>There are two dining options at the hotel including Swen’s Restaurant, which offers both communal and family seating. The menu is globally-inspired and makes use of regionally-sourced ingredients. Some of the top dishes include the grilled bone-in pork chop, rigatoni bolognese, and mac and cheese with ham and English peas. The Gulch Pub is also available with handcrafted drinks.</p>
<p>The Snowpine Lodge also houses Stillwell Spa where guests can enjoy beauty treatments, massage, waxing, and facials, among other things. There is also a steam room and sauna to enjoy relaxing. Guests preparing for events can make sure of makeup artists and stylists to ensure the day goes off without a hitch.</p></div><div class="b40a-button-container"><button role="button" class="Iqt3 Iqt3-mod-bold Button-No-Standard-Style Iqt3-mod-variant-outline Iqt3-mod-theme-base Iqt3-mod-shape-rounded-small Iqt3-mod-shape-mod-default Iqt3-mod-spacing-default Iqt3-mod-size-small" tabindex="0" aria-disabled="false"><div class="Iqt3-button-container"><div class="Iqt3-button-content">Read more</div></div><div class="Iqt3-button-focus-outline"></div></button></div></div><div class="b40a-section-container b40a-rating-container"><div class="b40a-rating-info"><div class="b40a-rating-box b40a-great"><div class="b40a-rating-score">8.5</div></div><div class="b40a-rating-summary"><div class="b40a-rating-category">Very good rating</div><div class="b40a-rating-count">Based on 67 verified guest reviews</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role="region" aria-label="Prices" tabindex="-1"><span id="navbar-item-rooms" class="vlX0-section-scroll-position" style="top:-100px"></span><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="-section" style="top:-80px" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-separator Vdvb-mod-color-default"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">Latest deals for The Snowpine Lodge</h2></div><div data-section-name="rates" class="zI2F"><div><div class="RY0w"><div class="RY0w-searchFormContainer"><div class="RY0w-datesAndRoomsGuests"><div class="RY0w-dates"><div><div class="cBaN"><div class="cBaN-date-select-wrapper"><div class="jZyL jZyL-mod-size-default"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="JONo-button" aria-label="Se