ss="acD_-comment-label">Pros (+)<!-- --> </span><span id="showMoreText-31986">Convenience, Dinners were great, staff was warm and helpful. Very pleased. Stayined in the dorms with friends.</span></div></div><div class="c1Z-2-pagination"><nav aria-labelledby="pagination-u7647" class="Joiu Joiu-mod-variant-action Joiu-with-label"><div id="pagination-u7647" class="Joiu-label">Showing 1-10 of 67 reviews</div><div class="Joiu-buttons"><button role="button" class="Iqt3 Iqt3-mod-disabled Button-No-Standard-Style Iqt3-mod-variant-none Iqt3-mod-theme-light Iqt3-mod-shape-rounded-small Iqt3-mod-shape-mod-default Iqt3-mod-spacing-default Iqt3-mod-size-default" tabindex="-1" disabled="" aria-disabled="true" aria-label="Previous page"><div class="Iqt3-button-container"><div class="Iqt3-button-content"><div class="A8fY-chevron" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"><path d="M119.238 164.801c-53.425-64.11-55.449-63.064-50-69.603l50-60l11.523 9.603L84.763 100l45.999 55.199l-11.524 9.602z"/></svg></div></div></div><div class="Iqt3-button-focus-outline"></div></button><button role="button" id="active" class="Iqt3 Iqt3-mod-bold Button-No-Standard-Style Iqt3-mod-variant-solid Iqt3-mod-theme-action Iqt3-mod-shape-rounded-small Iqt3-mod-shape-mod-default Iqt3-mod-spacing-default Iqt3-mod-size-small" tabindex="-1" aria-disabled="false" aria-pressed="true" aria-label="Page 1"><div class="Iqt3-button-container"><div class="Iqt3-button-content">1</div></div><div class="Iqt3-button-focus-outline"></div></button><button role="button" class="Iqt3 Button-No-Standard-Style Iqt3-mod-variant-solid Iqt3-mod-theme-none Iqt3-mod-shape-rounded-small Iqt3-mod-shape-mod-default Iqt3-mod-spacing-default Iqt3-mod-size-small" tabindex="0" aria-disabled="false" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="Page 2"><div class="Iqt3-button-container"><div class="Iqt3-button-content">2</div></div><div class="Iqt3-button-focus-outline">