.64 1.91v9.9H80.22v-9.9l-.64-1.92c-2.3-6.91-5.54-13.53-10.16-19.16c-6.81-8.29-10.33-19.39-8.51-31.31c2.63-17.26 17-31.06 34.34-33.09c1.61-.19 3.2-.28 4.77-.28c21.86 0 39.58 17.72 39.58 39.58zm-19.79 71.91v-3.96H80.22v3.96c0 4.37 3.54 7.92 7.92 7.92h23.75c4.37 0 7.92-3.54 7.92-7.92zM105.95 41.62V25.79a5.94 5.94 0 00-11.88 0v15.83a5.94 5.94 0 0011.88 0z"/></svg></span><p class="qvba-title">Utilize the Ski Shop/Rental</p></div><p class="qvba-content">Guests appreciated the convenience of the ski shop/rental inside the hotel, making it easy to access skiing equipment.</p></div><div class="qvba"><div class="qvba-header"><span class="TDKK TDKK-mod-color-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"><path d="M34.88 144.53c-2.05 0-4.05-1.06-5.14-2.97a5.935 5.935 0 012.17-8.11l13.71-7.92c2.84-1.64 6.47-.67 8.11 2.17s.67 6.47-2.17 8.11l-13.71 7.92c-.94.54-1.96.8-2.96.8zm12.5-52.82a5.94 5.94 0 00-4.82-6.88l-15.59-2.75a5.94 5.94 0 00-2.06 11.7l15.59 2.75a5.941 5.941 0 006.88-4.82zm18.28-31.65a5.932 5.932 0 00.73-8.36L56.21 39.57c-2.11-2.51-5.86-2.84-8.36-.73a5.932 5.932 0 00-.73 8.36L57.3 59.33a5.935 5.935 0 008.36.73zm77.06-.73L152.9 47.2a5.932 5.932 0 00-.73-8.36a5.932 5.932 0 00-8.36.73L133.63 51.7a5.932 5.932 0 00.73 8.36a5.933 5.933 0 008.36-.73zm16.79 37.2l15.59-2.75c3.23-.57 5.38-3.65 4.82-6.88c-.57-3.23-3.67-5.38-6.88-4.82l-15.59 2.75c-3.23.57-5.38 3.65-4.82 6.88a5.95 5.95 0 006.88 4.82zm10.77 45.03c1.64-2.84.67-6.47-2.17-8.11l-13.71-7.92a5.937 5.937 0 00-5.94 10.28l13.71 7.92c.94.54 1.96.8 2.96.8c2.05 0 4.05-1.06 5.14-2.97zm-30.69-41.23c0 9.64-3.45 18.46-9.17 25.32c-4.6 5.52-7.71 12.13-9.98 18.95l-.64 1.91v9.9H80.22v-9.9l-.64-1.92c-2.3-6.91-5.54-13.53-10.16-19.16c-6.81-8.29-10.33-19.39-8.51-31.31c2.63-17.26 17-31.06 34.34-33.09c1.61-.19 3.2-.28 4.77-.28c21.86 0 39.58 17.72 39.58 39.58zm-19.79 71.91v-3.96H80.22v3.96c0 4.37 3.54 7.92 7.92 7.92h23.75c4.37 0 7.92-3.54 7.92-7.92zM105.95 41.62V25.79a5.94 5.94 0 00-11.88 0v15.83a5.94 5.94 0 0011.88 0z"/></svg></span><p class="qvba-title">Be Mindful of Third-Party Bookings</p></div><p class="qvba-content">Some guests reported a less favorable experience with check-in when booking through third-party platforms, so it may be worth considering booking directly with the hotel.</p></div><div class="qvba"><div class="qvba-header"><span class="TDKK TDKK-mod-color-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"><path d="M34.88 144.53c-2.05 0-4.05-1.06-5.14-2.97a5.935 5.935 0 012.17-8.11l13.71-7.92c2.84-1.64 6.47-.67 8.11 2.17s.67 6.47-2.17 8.11l-13.71 7.92c-.94.54-1.96.8-2.96.8zm12.5-52.82a5.94 5.94 0 00-4.82-6.88l-15.59-2.75a5.94 5.94 0 00-2.06 11.7l15.59 2.75a5.941 5.941 0 006.88-4.82zm18.28-31.65a5.932 5.932 0 00.73-8.36L56.21 39.57c-2.11-2.51-5.86-2.84-8.36-.73a5.932 5.932 0 00-.73 8.36L57.3 59.33a5.935 5.935 0 008.36.73zm77.06-.73L152.9 47.2a5.932 5.932 0 00-.73-8.36a5.932 5.932 0 00-8.36.73L133.63 51.7a5.932 5.932 0 00.73 8.36a5.933 5.933 0 008.36-.73zm16.79 37.2l15.59-2.75c3.23-.57 5.38-3.65 4.82-6.88c-.57-3.23-3.67-5.38-6.88-4.82l-15.59 2.75c-3.23.57-5.38 3.65-4.82 6.88a5.95 5.95 0 006.88 4.82zm10.77 45.03c1.64-2.84.67-6.47-2.17-8.11l-13.71-7.92a5.937 5.937 0 00-5.94 10.28l13.71 7.92c.94.54 1.96.8 2.96.8c2.05 0 4.05-1.06 5.14-2.97zm-30.69-41.23c0 9.64-3.45 18.46-9.17 25.32c-4.6 5.52-7.71 12.13-9.98 18.95l-.64 1.91v9.9H80.22v-9.9l-.64-1.92c-2.3-6.91-5.54-13.53-10.16-19.16c-6.81-8.29-10.33-19.39-8.51-31.31c2.63-17.26 17-31.06 34.34-33.09c1.61-.19 3.2-.28 4.77-.28c21.86 0 39.58 17.72 39.58 39.58zm-19.79 71.91v-3.96H80.22v3.96c0 4.37 3.54 7.92 7.92 7.92h23.75c4.37 0 7.92-3.54 7.92-7.92zM105.95 41.62V25.79a5.94 5.94 0 00-11.88 0v15.83a5.94 5.94 0 0011.88 0z"/></svg></span><p class="qvba-title">Enjoy the Heated Pool and Hot Tub</p></div><p class="qvba-content">Many guests enjoyed the heated pool and hot tub with a view, so be sure to take advantage of these facilities during your stay.</p></div><div class="qvba"><div class="qvba-header"><span class="TDKK TDKK-mod-color-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"><path d="M34.88 144.53c-2.05 0-4.05-1.06-5.14-2.97a5.935 5.935 0 012.17-8.11l13.71-7.92c2.84-1.64 6.47-.67 8.11 2.17s.67 6.47-2.17 8.11l-13.71 7.92c-.94.54-1.96.8-2.96.8zm12.5-52.82a5.94 5.94 0 00-4.82-6.88l-15.59-2.75a5.94 5.94 0 00-2.06 11.7l15.59 2.75a5.941 5.941 0 006.88-4.82zm18.28-31.65a5.932 5.932 0 00.73-8.36L56.21 39.57c-2.11-2.51-5.86-2.84-8.36-.73a5.932 5.932 0 00-.73 8.36L57.3 59.33a5.935 5.935 0 008.36.73zm77.06-.73L152.9 47.2a5.932 5.932 0 00-.73-8.36a5.932 5.932 0 00-8.36.73L133.63 51.7a5.932 5.932 0 00.73 8.36a5.933 5.933 0 008.36-.73zm16.79 37.2l15.59-2.75c3.23-.57 5.38-3.65 4.82-6.88c-.57-3.23-3.67-5.38-6.88-4.82l-15.59 2.75c-3.23.57-5.38 3.65-4.82 6.88a5.95 5.95 0 006.88 4.82zm10.77 45.03c1.64-2.84.67-6.47-2.17-8.11l-13.71-7.92a5.937 5.937 0 00-5.94 10.28l13.71 7.92c.94.54 1.96.8 2.96.8c2.05 0 4.05-1.06 5.14-2.97zm-30.69-41.23c0 9.64-3.45 18.46-9.17 25.32c-4.6 5.52-7.71 12.13-9.98 18.95l-.64 1.91v9.9H80.22v-9.9l-.64-1.92c-2.3-6.91-5.54-13.53-10.16-19.16c-6.81-8.29-10.33-19.39-8.51-31.31c2.63-17.26 17-31.06 34.34-33.09c1.61-.19 3.2-.28 4.77-.28c21.86 0 39.58 17.72 39.58 39.58zm-19.79 71.91v-3.96H80.22v3.96c0 4.37 3.54 7.92 7.92 7.92h23.75c4.37 0 7.92-3.54 7.92-7.92zM105.95 41.62V25.79a5.94 5.94 0 00-11.88 0v15.83a5.94 5.94 0 0011.88 0z"/></svg></span><p class="qvba-title">Consider Communication with Management</p></div><p class="qvba-content">In case of any issues with the room or services, it may be beneficial to maintain clear communication with the management to address and resolve any concerns promptly.</p></div><div class="qvba"><div class="qvba-header"><span class="TDKK TDKK-mod-color-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation"><path 