Angle:90deg;--shimmerDuration:2s"></div></div><div class="clMY-address">Exact location provided after booking</div><h3 class="clMY-location-header">What&#x27;s nearby</h3><ul><li class="c96-Q-location"><span class="c96-Q-location-name">Alta Ski Area</span><span class="c96-Q-location-distance">0.8 mi</span></li><li class="c96-Q-location"><span class="c96-Q-location-name">Snowbird Tram</span><span class="c96-Q-location-distance">1.4 mi</span></li><li class="c96-Q-location"><span class="c96-Q-location-name">Snowbird</span><span class="c96-Q-location-distance">1.5 mi</span></li><li class="c96-Q-location"><span class="c96-Q-location-name">Twin Peaks</span><span class="c96-Q-location-distance">4.8 mi</span></li><li class="c96-Q-location"><span class="c96-Q-location-name">Pfeifferhorn</span><span class="c96-Q-location-distance">5.5 mi</span></li></ul></section></div></div><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="-section" style="top:0" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-separator Vdvb-mod-color-default"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">Policies</h2></div><table class="Q6C3-table"><tbody class="kml-row"><tr class="kml-col-6-12-m"><th class="Q6C3-title-wrapper"><h3 class="Q6C3-title">Check-in/Check-out</h3></th><td class="Q6C3-description">Check in anytime after 4:00 PM, check out anytime before 10:00 AM</td></tr><tr class="kml-col-6-12-m"><th class="Q6C3-title-wrapper"><h3 class="Q6C3-title">Cancellation/prepayment</h3></th><td class="Q6C3-description">Cancellation/prepayment policies vary by room type and provider.</td></tr></tbody></table></section></div><div role="region" aria-label="When to book" tabindex="-1"><span id="navbar-item-when-to-book" class="vlX0-section-scroll-position" style="top:-100px"></span><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="-section" style="top:0" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-separator Vdvb-mod-color-default"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">Essential information about The Snowpine Lodge</h2></div><div class="AWKa AWKa-pres-kayak"><table class="AWKa-table" style="grid-column:span 4"><tbody class="AWKa-table-body"><tr class="AWKa-table-row"><th class="AWKa-item-header AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><h3 class="AWKa-item-title">Low season</h3></th><th class="AWKa-item-header AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><h3 class="AWKa-item-title">High season</h3></th><th class="AWKa-item-header AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><h3 class="AWKa-item-title">Average price (weeknight)</h3></th><th class="AWKa-item-header AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><h3 class="AWKa-item-title">Average price (weekend night)</h3></th></tr><tr class="AWKa-table-row"><td class="AWKa-item-data"><div class="AWKa-item-content">June</div></td><td class="AWKa-item-data"><div class="AWKa-item-content">February</div></td><td class="AWKa-item-data"><div class="AWKa-item-content">$395</div></td><td class="AWKa-item-data"><div class="AWKa-item-content">$438</div></td></tr><tr class="AWKa-table-row"><td class="AWKa-item-extra AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><div class="AWKa-item-description">Cheapest month to stay with an average <b>49%</b> drop in price.</div></td><td class="AWKa-item-extra AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><div class="AWKa-item-description">Most expensive month to stay with an average <b>133%</b> rise in price.</div></td><td class="AWKa-item-extra AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><div class="AWKa-item-description">Average <b>Sun - Thu</b> price over the last 2 weeks.</div></td><td class="AWKa-item-extra AWKa-mod-border-radius-xlarge"><div class="AWKa-item-description">Average <b>Fri & Sat</b> price over the last 2 weeks.</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="AWKa-slide"></div><div class="AWKa-slide"></div><div class="AWKa-slide"></div><div class="AWKa-slide"></div></div></section></div><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="-section" style="top:0" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-separator Vdvb-mod-color-default GHOV"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">When to book a room at The Snowpine Lodge</h2></div><div class="GHOV-explanation">Price per night. Prices are not fixed and may vary with time.</div><div class="kml-row"><div class="kml-col-12-12 kml-col-6-12-l"><div class="GHOV-chart-title">Average nightly price per month</div><div class="l6Lz l6Lz-mod-spacing-none l6Lz-mod-border-radius-none l6Lz-mod-position-relative l6Lz-mod-color-default" style="height:288px;--shimmerAnimationDelay:0ms;--shimmerAngle:90deg;--shimmerDuration:2s"></div></div><div class="kml-col-12-12 kml-col-6-12-l"><div class="GHOV-chart-title">Average nightly price</div><div class="l6Lz l6Lz-mod-spacing-none l6Lz-mod-border-radius-none l6Lz-mod-position-relative l6Lz-mod-color-default" style="height:288px;--shimmerAnimationDelay:0ms;--shimmerAngle:90deg;--shimmerDuration:2s"></div></div></div></section></div></div><div role="region" aria-label="Tips &amp; FAQs" tabindex="-1"><span id="navbar-item-tips-and-faqs" class="vlX0-section-scroll-position" style="top:-100px"></span><div class="ZJPR-tips-wrapper"><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="tips-section" style="top:0" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="tips" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-separator Vdvb-mod-color-default"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">KAYAK&#x27;s top tips for your stay at The Snowpine Lodge</h2></div><div class="ZJPR-tips-wrapper"><div class="KNh0"><ul class="KNh0-expandable"><li class="KNh0-item"><span style="transform:translate3d(0,0,0);vertical-align:middle;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;width:20px;height:20px" class="KNh0-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" style="width:inherit;height:inherit;line-height:inherit;color:inherit"><path d="M100 20c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80s80-35.817 80-80s-35.817-80-80-80zm-8.403 114.801c-8.222 8.896-16.39-1.147-38.097-17.752l12.132-15.697l17.483 13.375L131.85 62l14.65 13.401l-54.903 59.4z"/></svg></span><div>If you’re after a cheap room at The Snowpine Lodge, then you should consider staying during the low season. The cheapest deals can generally be found in June and April.</div></li><li class="KNh0-item"><span style="transform:translate3d(0,0,0);vertical-align:middle;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;width:20px;height:20px" class="KNh0-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" style="width:inherit;height:inherit;line-height:inherit;color:inherit"><path d="M100 20c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80s80-35.817 80-80s-35.817-80-80-80zm-8.403 114.801c-8.222 8.896-16.39-1.147-38.097-17.752l12.132-15.697l17.483 13.375L131.85 62l14.65 13.401l-54.903 59.4z"/></svg></span><div>Prices can also vary depending on which day of the week you stay. For the best room deals at The Snowpine Lodge, plan to stay on a Tuesday or Wednesday. The most expensive day is usually Thursday.</div></li><li class="KNh0-item"><span style="transform:translate3d(0,0,0);vertical-align:middle;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;width:20px;height:20px" class="KNh0-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" style="width:inherit;height:inherit;line-height:inherit;color:inherit"><path d="M100 20c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80s80-35.817 80-80s-35.817-80-80-80zm-8.403 114.801c-8.222 8.896-16.39-1.147-38.097-17.752l12.132-15.697l17.483 13.375L131.85 62l14.65 13.401l-54.903 59.4z"/></svg></span><div>The cheapest price a room at The Snowpine Lodge was booked for on KAYAK in the last 2 weeks was $273, while the most expensive was $477.</div></li><li class="KNh0-item"><span style="transform:translate3d(0,0,0);vertical-align:middle;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;width:20px;height:20px" class="KNh0-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" style="width:inherit;height:inherit;line-height:inherit;color:inherit"><path d="M100 20c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80s80-35.817 80-80s-35.817-80-80-80zm-8.403 114.801c-8.222 8.896-16.39-1.147-38.097-17.752l12.132-15.697l17.483 13.375L131.85 62l14.65 13.401l-54.903 59.4z"/></svg></span><div>How long should you stay at The Snowpine Lodge? KAYAK users usually book their rooms here for 2 days.</div></li></ul><div class="hkp9 hkp9-mod-variant-stretch"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="hkp9-button">See more tips</div></div></div></div></section></div></div><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="faqs-section" style="top:0" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="faqs" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-color-default"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">FAQs when booking at The Snowpine Lodge</h2></div><ul class="c5Aix c5Aix-mod-variant-default c5Aix-mod-visible-faqs-default c5Aix-expandable"><li class="c9xAl c9xAl-theme-default c9xAl-mod-variant-default c9xAl-mod-size-base c9xAl-mod-separator"><details open="" class="HABP"><summary class="HABP-button"><h4 class="c9xAl-question">Where is The Snowpine Lodge located?</h4><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="HABP-chevron HABP-mod-thin HABP-pres-theme-dark" role="presentation"><path d="M100 132.5c-3.873 0 .136 2.376-64.801-51.738l9.603-11.523L100 115.237l55.199-45.999l9.603 11.523C99.806 134.924 103.855 132.5 100 132.5z"/></svg></summary><p id="hotelLocationFaq" class="HABP-content c9xAl-answer">The Snowpine Lodge is located at , 0.3 miles from the center of Alta. Alta Ski Area is the closest landmark to The Snowpine Lodge.</p></details></li><li class="c9xAl c9xAl-theme-default c9xAl-mod-variant-default c9xAl-mod-size-base c9xAl-mod-separator"><details open="" class="HABP"><summary class="HABP-button"><h4 class="c9xAl-question">When is check-in time and check-out time at The Snowpine Lodge?</h4><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="HABP-chevron HABP-mod-thin HABP-pres-theme-dark" role="presentation"><path d="M100 132.5c-3.873 0 .136 2.376-64.801-51.738l9.603-11.523L100 115.237l55.199-45.999l9.603 11.523C99.806 134.924 103.855 132.5 100 132.5z"/></svg></summary><p id="hotelCheckinCheckoutFaq" class="HABP-content c9xAl-answer">Check-in time is 4:00 PM and check-out time is 10:00 AM at The Snowpine Lodge.</p></details></li><li class="c9xAl c9xAl-theme-default c9xAl-mod-variant-default c9xAl-mod-size-base c9xAl-mod-separator"><details class="HABP"><summary class="HABP-button"><h4 class="c9xAl-question">Does The Snowpine Lodge offer free Wi-Fi?</h4><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="HABP-chevron HABP-mod-thin HABP-pres-theme-dark" role="presentation"><path d="M100 132.5c-3.873 0 .136 2.376-64.801-51.738l9.603-11.523L100 115.237l55.199-45.999l9.603 11.523C99.806 134.924 103.855 132.5 100 132.5z"/></svg></summary><p id="hotelFreeWifiFaq" class="HABP-content c9xAl-answer">Yes, The Snowpine Lodge offers free Wi-Fi.</p></details></li><li class="c9xAl c9xAl-theme-default c9xAl-mod-variant-default c9xAl-mod-size-base c9xAl-mod-separator"><details class="HABP"><summary class="HABP-button"><h4 class="c9xAl-question">How far is The Snowpine Lodge from the airport?</h4><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="HABP-chevron HABP-mod-thin HABP-pres-theme-dark" role="presentation"><path d="M100 132.5c-3.873 0 .136 2.376-64.801-51.738l9.603-11.523L100 115.237l55.199-45.999l9.603 11.523C99.806 134.924 103.855 132.5 100 132.5z"/></svg></summary><p id="hotelDistanceToAirportFaq" class="HABP-content c9xAl-answer">The Snowpine Lodge is 22.7 miles from Salt Lake City. The Snowpine Lodge is 26.4 miles from Provo.</p></details></li><li class="c9xAl c9xAl-theme-default c9xAl-mod-variant-default c9xAl-mod-size-base c9xAl-mod-separator"><details class="HABP"><summary class="HABP-button"><h4 class="c9xAl-question">Does The Snowpine Lodge have a pool?</h4><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="HABP-chevron HABP-mod-thin HABP-pres-theme-dark" role="presentation"><path d="M100 132.5c-3.873 0 .136 2.376-64.801-51.738l9.603-11.523L100 115.237l55.199-45.999l9.603 11.523C99.806 134.924 103.855 132.5 100 132.5z"/></svg></summary><p id="hotelPoolFaq" class="HABP-content c9xAl-answer">Yes, The Snowpine Lodge has a pool onsite.</p></details></li><li class="c9xAl c9xAl-theme-default c9xAl-mod-variant-default c9xAl-mod-size-base c9xAl-mod-separator"><details class="HABP"><summary class="HABP-button"><h4 class="c9xAl-question">How does KAYAK find such great The Snowpine Lodge hotel deals?</h4><svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="1.25em" height="1.25em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="HABP-chevron HABP-mod-thin HABP-pres-theme-dark" role="presentation"><path d="M100 132.5c-3.873 0 .136 2.376-64.801-51.738l9.603-11.523L100 115.237l55.199-45.999l9.603 11.523C99.806 134.924 103.855 132.5 100 132.5z"/></svg></summary><p id="greatDealsFaq" class="HABP-content c9xAl-answer">KAYAK scours the web for all room deals available at The Snowpine Lodge in Alta and lets you compare them to find the best rate for your stay. Many different travel sites will offer discounts or deals at different times for rooms at The Snowpine Lodge and KAYAK will provide you with prices from a huge range of travel sites. That means that you can always find a great deal for The Snowpine Lodge.</p></details></li></ul><div class="c5Aix-button-wrapper"><div class="hkp9 hkp9-mod-variant-default"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="hkp9-button">See more FAQs</div></div></div></section></div></div><div role="region" aria-label="Nearby stays" tabindex="-1"><span id="navbar-item-nearby-stays" class="vlX0-section-scroll-position" style="top:-100px"></span><div class="kml-layout edges-m mobile-edges c31EJ"><span id="-section" style="top:0" class="Vdvb-section-scroll-position"></span><section id="" class="Vdvb Vdvb-mod-size-desktop-large-mobile-standard Vdvb-mod-separator Vdvb-mod-color-default"><div class="Vdvb-header-container" data-testid="header"><h2 class="Vdvb-title">Nearby hotels and places to stay</h2></div><div class="Rupq"><div class="Rupq-heading"><div class="kml-row"><h3 class="Rupq-title kml-col-6-12">Closest</h3><a href="#" class="ZT1E-anchor-reset Rupq-link kml-col-6-12">See more nearby stays</a></div></div><div class="c9ivc"><div class="M3KI M3KI-mod-stop-normal M3KI-mod-radius-none M3KI-mod-snap-enabled AP2R-var-spacing-none c6BEx c6BEx-quarter"><div class="M3KI-slide" data-testid="data-test-slide data-test-slide-inactive"><div class="c9ivc-hotel-wrapper"><div class="Wys1"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="Wys1-img-label-wrapper" aria-label="See deals for Luxury Alta Utah Home with Hot Tub, Pool Table, Game Room and Chef&#x27;s Kitchen, a hotel with rates from $2,317+"><div class="Wys1-fallback-img-wrapper"><span style="transform:translate3d(0,0,0);vertical-align:middle;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale" class="Wys1-fallback-img"><svg width="100%" height="100%" version="1.1" id="Layer_1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/