e Lodge in Alta (Utah) on KAYAK. Rates from $194.","ogTitle":null,"ogDescription":null,"ogImage":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontent.r9cdn.net\u002Frimg\u002Fhimg\u002Ff0\u002F84\u002Fbb\u002Fexpedia_group-495978-26cda8fa-748178.jpg?width=1200&height=630&crop=true","twitterTitle":null,"twitterDescription":null,"twitterImage":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontent.r9cdn.net\u002Frimg\u002Fhimg\u002Ff0\u002F84\u002Fbb\u002Fexpedia_group-495978-26cda8fa-748178.jpg?width=440&height=220&crop=true","deeplink":"android-app:\u002F\u002Fcom.kayak.android\u002Fhttp\u002Fwww.kayak.com\u002Fdeeplinks\u002Fhotels\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge-c40612-h495978-details","naverMetaKeywords":null,"canonical":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.com\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp","alternates":[{"hreflang":"de-DE","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.de\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"es-ES","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.es\u002FAlta-Hoteles-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"fr-FR","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.fr\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"en-GB","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.co.uk\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"it-IT","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.it\u002FHotel-a-Alta-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"en-US","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.com\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"ca-ES","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.cat\u002FAlta-Hotels-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"es-US","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.es.kayak.com\u002FAlta-Hoteles-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"},{"hreflang":"es-UY","href":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.kayak.com.uy\u002FAlta-Hoteles-The-Snowpine-Lodge.495978.ksp"}],"lowestPrice":null,"alternativeTitle":null},"experiments":["seo-kayak-hotel-details-chatgpt-faqs-tips=enabled","seo-kayak-hdp-header-redesign=control-group","seo-kayak-hdp-automatic-deal-update=disabled","seo-kayak-hotel-details-chatgpt-short-description=control-group","seo-kayak-hdp-footer-blackout=enabled","seo-kayak-hdp-add-cmp2=enabled","seo-hotel-details-shared-ui-form=disabled"],"startDateOffset":7,"endDateOffset":8,"contentState":{"smartyLocationName":"The Snowpine Lodge - Alta, UT","coverImageUrl":"\u002Frimg\u002Fhimg\u002Ff0\u002F84\u002Fbb\u002Fexpedia_group-495978-26cda8fa-748178.jpg?width=1366&height=768&crop=true","faqLinksLimit":0,"hotelId":"495978","hotelName":"The Snowpine Lodge","cityId":"40612","faqs":[{"questionId":"hotelLocationFaq","question":"Where is The Snowpine Lodge located?","answer":"The Snowpine Lodge is located at , 0.3 miles from the center of Alta. Alta Ski Area is the closest landmark to The Snowpine Lodge."},{"questionId":"hotelCheckinCheckoutFaq","question":"When is check-in time and check-out time at The Snowpine Lodge?","answer":"Check-in time is 4:00 PM and check-out time is 10:00 AM at The Snowpine Lodge."},{"questionId":"hotelFreeWifiFaq","question":"Does The Snowpine Lodge offer free Wi-Fi?","answer":"Yes, The Snowpine Lodge offers free Wi-Fi."},{"questionId":"hotelDistanceToAirportFaq","question":"How far is The Snowpine Lodge from the airport?","answer":"The Snowpine Lodge is 22.7 miles from Salt Lake City. The Snowpine Lodge is 26.4 miles from Provo."},{"questionId":"greatDealsFaq","question":"How does KAYAK find such great The Snowpine Lodge hotel deals?","answer":"KAYAK scours the web for all room deals available at The Snowpine Lodge in Alta and lets you compare them to find the best rate for your stay. Many different travel sites will offer discounts or deals at different times for rooms at The Snowpine Lodge and KAYAK will provide you with prices from a huge range of travel sites. That means that you can always find a great deal for The Snowpine Lodge."},{"questionId":"hotelPoolFaq","question":"Does The Snowpine Lodge have a pool?","answer":"Yes, The Snowpine Lodge has a pool onsite."}],"tips":["If you’re after a cheap room at The Snowpine Lodge, then you should consider staying during the low season. The cheapest deals can generally be found in June and April.","Prices can also vary depending on which day of the week you stay. For the best room deals at The Snowpine Lodge, plan to stay on a Tuesday or Wednesday. The most expensive day is usually Thursday.","The cheapest price a room at The Snowpine Lodge was booked for on KAYAK in the last 2 weeks was $273, while the most expensive was $477.","How long should you stay at The Snowpine Lodge? KAYAK users usually book their rooms here for 2 days."],"faqsAi":[{"header":"What dining options are available at The Snowpine Lodge?","content":"The hotel offers two dining options including Swen’s Restaurant, which offers globally-inspired dishes made with regionally-sourced ingredients, and The Gulch Pub with handcrafted drinks."},{"header":"What are the amenities offered at The Snowpine Lodge?","content":"The hotel offers a fitness center, yoga studio, heated outdoor pool, jetted spas, basketball hoops, volleyball net, outdoor firepits, ski lockers, and Stillwell Spa offering beauty treatments, massage, waxing, and facials."},{"header":"What can guests expect from the hotel's staff and service?","content":"Guests can expect friendly, happy, and helpful staff who go beyond to ensure a wonderful experience. However, there have been instances of inconsistent service quality that the hotel is working to address."},{"header":"What are the nearby attractions to The Snowpine Lodge?","content":"Nearby attractions include Alta Ski Area, Snowbird Tram, Snowbird, Twin Peaks, and Pfeifferhorn."},{"header":"What are the common concerns about The Snowpine Lodge?","content":"Some common concerns include limited food options, noise from neighboring rooms, and inconsistent service quality. The hotel is working to address these concerns to ensure a better experience for all guests."}],"tipsAi":[{"header":"Opt for a Room with a View","content":"Several guests mentioned the great views of the mountain from the rooms, so consider choosing a room with a view for a more enjoyable stay."},{"header":"Consider Noise Levels","content":"Some guests reported that the walls were thin, and noise from neighboring rooms could be heard. If you are sensitive to noise, you may want to consider this when selecting your room."},{"header":"Check Room Amenities","content":"Before finalizing your room choice, ensure that the amenities, such as a bathtub and a couch, are as per your requirements, as some guests reported discrepancies in the room features."},{"header":"Bring Snacks","content":"While the hotel offers dining options, some guests suggested bringing your own snacks, especially for after skiing, as there were limited food options available."},{"header":"Utilize the Ski Shop\u002FRental","content":"Guests appreciated the convenience of the ski shop\u002Frental inside the hotel, making it easy to access skiing equipment."},{"header":"Be Mindful of Third-Party Bookings","content":"Some guests reported a less favorable experience with check-in when booking through third-party platforms, so it may be worth considering booking directly with the hotel."},{"header":"Enjoy the Heated Pool and Hot Tub","content":"Many guests enjoyed the heated pool and hot tub with a view, so be sure to take advantage of these facilities during your stay."},{"header":"Consider Communication with Management","content":"In case of any issues with the room or services, it may be beneficial to maintain clear communication with the management to address and resolve any concerns promptly."},{"header":"Plan for Dining Options","content":"While the hotel offers dining facilities, some guests found the food and service to be inconsistent, so it may be helpful to explore nearby dining options as well."},{"header":"Take Advantage of Stillwell Spa","content":"Guests appreciated the spa facilities, including beauty treatments, massage, and more, so consider indulging in some relaxation at the spa during your stay."}],"policies":[{"type":"other","title":"Check-in\u002FCheck-out","dataText":"Check in anytime after 4:00 PM, check out anytime before 10:00 AM","description":null,"tooltipInfo":null,"additionalInfo":null,"provider":null,"airlineImageUrl":null,"dealInfo":null,"airlineCode":null},{"type":"other","title":"Cancellation\u002Fprepayment","dataText":"Cancellation\u002Fprepayment policies vary by room type and provider.","description":null,"tooltipInfo":null,"additionalInfo":null,"provider":null,"airlineImageUrl":null,"dealInfo":null,"airlineCode":null}],"amenitiesData":{"topAmenities":[{"code":"mountain_view","localizedName":"Mountain view","icon":"region"},{"code":"outpool","localizedName":"Outdoor pool","icon":"pool"},{"code":"hottub","localizedName":"Hot tub","icon":"pool"},{"code":"sauna","localizedName":"Sauna","icon":"spa"},{"code":"gameroom","localizedName":"Game room","icon":"entertainment"},{"code":"pooltable","localizedName":"Pool table","icon":"entertainment"},{"code":"terrace\u002Fpatio","localizedName":"Terrace\u002FPatio","icon":"terrace"},{"code":"balcony","localizedName":"Balcony","icon":"city"},{"code":"ac","localizedName":"Air-conditioned","icon":"ac"},{"code":"laundryroom","localizedName":"Laundry facilities","icon":"laundry"}],"categorisedAmenities":[{"code":"bathroom","localizedName":"Bathroom","amenities":[{"code":"shower","localizedName":"Shower","icon":"shower"},{"code":"shower_cap","localizedName":"Shower cap","icon":"shower"},{"code":"additional_bathroom","localizedName":"Additional bathroom","icon":"check"},{"code":"additional_toilet","localizedName":"Additional toilet","icon":"check"},{"code":"bathtub","localizedName":"Bathtub","icon":"check"},{"code":"hairdryer","localizedName":"Hairdryer","icon":"check"},{"code":"toilet","localizedName":"Toilet","icon":"check"},{"code":"toilet_paper","localizedName":"Toilet paper","icon":"check"},{"code":"bathrobe","localizedName":"Bathrobe","icon":"check"},{"code":"private_bathroom","loc